Description :

1

Through some arcane wizardry I've conjured up a couple of big demons. They'd make an awesome addition to your army! Comes in 2 poses, both without wings or with separate wings so it should hopefully fit on your printer. I scaled them approximately to some of the bigger demons out there but nothing crazy, you might want them bigger. They just have 1 big axe each - if you're wanting more you can merge or glue something on easily since they both have an empty fist.

He's so angry, but yet, so tiny! The Amateur Phlebotomist, who loves to draw blood from his friends!

Option for Bare Head or Helm.

Check out the "_standoffs" version. The models' feet are offset from the plug, allowing you to use the plug as a stand when painting, and then slice or snip off the small cylinders to allow you to glue the feet directly onto the base, for a seamless finish.

Thanks to Moonjammy, for the base models, and MrMcAngry for the base bare head.

If you'd like to commision a custom character or kit, please contact me on Discord under "Dafydd".

If you'd like to keep up with my current projects, and support the modelling work I do, please check out my patreon at: www.patreon.com/Daffmakes
